tool_description:
Details for NSW Strata Properties,

Lookup an individual plan or find plans within a suburb or local government area.
name: NSW Strata Details
title: NSW Strata Details

api_list.name: List Of Suburbs
api_list.description: Retrieve a list of all of the suburbs and the number of strata plans within that suburb.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://nsw-strata-details.p.rapidapi.com/suburbs/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "nsw-strata-details.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: Strata Plan Details
api_list.description: Retrieve a single strata plan including 2021 Australian Census dervied data  for both the suburb and local government areas.

api_list.name: Strata Plans Within A Local Government Area (LGA)
api_list.description: Retrieve a list of all of the strata plans that are within a specific local government area including 2021 Australian Census dervied data .

api_list.name: List Of Local Government Areas
api_list.description: Retrieve a list of all of the local government areas  and the number of strata plans within that local government area.

api_list.name: Strata Plans Within A Suburb
api_list.description: Retrieve a list of all of the strata plans that are within a specific suburb including 2021 Australian Census dervied data .

required_parameters.name: suburb
required_parameters.description: see the `/suburbs/` call for a list of all of the suburbs and the number of strata plans.

optional_parameters.name: page
optional_parameters.description:
If a search spans more than one page, then this will paginate through the result.

The current page number and number of pages will be returned in the `response` JSON Object with the keys:

 - `page` - the current page number
 - `num_pages` - the number of pages within the result set
